# anushapt

!!Eduard Konstantinov - Anushka's father, who is known as being a hard and dangerous man. Since marrying Valeria and starting a family, he has mellowed out slightly, but he is still someone you don't want to piss off. In his youth, he was the leader of a local gang that would cause mayhem and chaos wherever they went. Surprisingly, he's managed to avoid spending any time behind bars.

!!Valeria Konstantinov - Anushka's mother, who enjoyed being a bad girl and a heart breaker in her youth. Ironically, she is now a wife and mother of three, which she has come to resent. More often than not, she has nothing good to say about her family. Still living in the fantasy that she's still a youthful heart breaker makes her a hot topic among the rumormongers in the town that she flirts with a lot of men, but none of them are willing to risk fooling around with her as long as Eduard is her husband.

!!Maksim Konstantinov - Anushka's younger brother, who is four years younger than her. Until recently, he was considered a good kid, but now he has started to notice girls, bully other kids at school, and hassle old people in town. He seems to idolize Radomir, often saying he wants to be just like him.

!!Timofey Konstantinov - Anushka's youngest brother, who is a couple years younger than Maksim. Unlike his brother, he is still doing great in school and is seen as the nicer sibling compared to Maksim. When he isn't following his brother around, he is often found playing with the other kids or riding his skateboard around the apartment complex.

!AnushkaLoc tells us where Anushka is located
!----------------------------------------------
