				'You smile and do you best to reassure him as he seems to be honestly worried about her. "She has a good head on her shoulders, I am sure she knows just how far she can push things."'
				*nl
				'He shakes his head slightly. "If it was only that easy, but you girls still don''t know just how dangerous the world is and it only takes one mistake or even just being in the wrong place or meeting the wrong person that can change you life for ever and not in a good way."'
